{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SnWZHqWqX6Ggnuxu5XtpEE","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→## WHY\n     2→\n     3→Retrospectives produced vague observations without actionable items, and\n     4→verification pipeline issues (hangs, false positives, verify-dev loops) were\n     5→not systematically tracked. This patch structures retro analysis around\n     6→verification effectiveness, pipeline health, documentation accuracy, test\n     7→quality trends, and mandatory concrete action items with owners.\n     8→(FR33, FR36, NFR20)\n     9→\n    10→## Codeharness Retrospective Quality Metrics\n    11→\n    12→### Verification Effectiveness\n    13→\n    14→- How many ACs were caught by black-box verification vs slipped through?\n    15→- Were there false positives (proof said PASS but feature was broken)?\n    16→- Were there false negatives (proof said FAIL but feature actually works)?\n    17→- Time spent on verification — is it proportional to value?\n    18→\n    19→### Verification Pipeline Health\n    20→\n    21→- Did the verifier hang on permissions? (check for `--allowedTools` issues)\n    22→- Did stories get stuck in verify→dev loops? (check `attempts` counter)\n    23→- Were stories incorrectly flagged as `integration-required`?\n    24→- Did the verify parser correctly detect `[FAIL]` verdicts?\n    25→\n    26→### Documentation Health\n    27→\n    28→- AGENTS.md accuracy for changed modules\n    29→- Exec-plans completeness for active stories\n    30→- Stale documentation identified and cleaned up\n    31→\n    32→### Test Quality\n    33→\n    34→- Coverage trend (improving, stable, declining)\n    35→- Any flaky tests introduced?\n    36→- Integration test coverage for cross-module interactions\n    37→\n    38→### Action Items\n    39→\n    40→Every retro MUST produce concrete action items with:\n    41→- Clear description of what to fix\n    42→- Why it matters (what fails without this fix)\n    43→- Owner and priority\n    44→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01WFzjRFzKVwYJKtrGR84YZ3","session_id":"4b69c0d8-c2d9-426d-9413-456ae301bb7e","uuid":"d6d2e947-3f7a-44b6-bbdd-5ecc67b26934","timestamp":"2026-03-28T13:40:46.277Z"}
