fy-parser.test.ts` has 15+ `.tier` assertions across `parseStoryACs` tests (lines 106, 111, 229, 232, 253-259, 278, 296, 312, 333-336, 357-360) |\n| AC12 | PASS | 152 test files, 4021 tests, 0 failures |\n\n### Step 6: Proof Document\nUpdated existing proof at `verification/16-8-update-all-tests-proof.md` with current test count (4021).\n\n### Step 7: Verify Command\n`npx codeharness verify --story 16-8-update-all-tests` returned `[OK] Story 16-8-update-all-tests: verified`.\n\n### Step 8: Final Result\n**ALL_PASS (12/12 ACs)**\n\n---\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 17\n- By tool: Bash: 6, Read: 3, Edit: 2, Grep: 6, Write: 0, other: 0\n- Largest Bash outputs (top 3 by line count): `npm test` (~321 lines), `npx vitest run --coverage` (~1017 lines saved to file), `npm run build` (~15 lines)\n- Files read: 3 unique, 4 total reads (vitest output file read 2x)\n- Redundant operations: vitest output file read twice at different offsets (necessary for extracting summary + coverage from large output); no wasted calls"}],"totalDurationMs":206557,"totalTokens":52739,"totalToolUseCount":24,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":224,"cache_read_input_tokens":51352,"output_tokens":1162,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":224},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
